{
  "stem": "16345.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next happened, it was amazing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I had heard that my aunt was treated much better.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Evidently, evidently, that old witch believed me when I told her I could have killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, beating up on her, not giving her her rations of food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, you could, you could kill somebody with harassment like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, many people died on the hand-- by the hands of other prisoners.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There, there were some kapos, let's say, in Auschwitz who, who really enjoyed murdering other prisoners.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were, for instance-- I, I once saw where two prison-- two prisoner kapos put one-- a long pole, which is sort of like a long baseball bat, on the throat of one prisoner.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And both of them stood on one-- each of them stood on one end of it until, until the, the person died.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were also going around and hitting people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- also, they were going around just hitting people indiscriminately.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let's say when we lined up our food, which was horrible-- line-- and not enough of it either-- who-- when we were crowding around, they started-- they sort of took one of those great big baseball bats and started hitting people in the head.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, I once got hit in the head.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I didn't wake up till the following day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We, we almost always got a piece of what they called bread every day and something that they called either coffee or tea.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And nobody could tell the difference.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we got soup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some of us became very adept at what we called organizing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like, I had a, a, a can that I attached a wire to.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
